The paper discusses deep learning, which is a subfield of machine learning and artificial intelligence. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are the most likely categories. The paper also touches on the theoretical aspects of deep learning, which could fall under cs.IT (Information Theory) and cs.CC (Computational Complexity). Finally, the paper discusses the role of neural networks, which could fall under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
